name: GS Trader
overview:
Established in 2007, G.S. Trader is known for its quality products in Tamil Nadu. The company is truly global and has achieved great heights in the trading and supplying domain of a comprehensive range of products which includes Cotton Clips, Cotton Waste and many more and manufacturer of Men’s and Women’s T-Shirts.

Our Product Range: Colored Yarn Waste Hosiery Yarn Waste Banian Waste Cotton Clippings Cotton Waste Cotton Clips Men’s T-Shirts Women’s T-Shirts

Infrastructure: The infrastructure that we have incorporated to support our daily activities have been tested for its performance and have been designed to speed up the production process. Our equipments are manufactured using superior technology which has helped us to increase the efficiency levels and surpass our competitors through our infrastructural strength and capability.

Our Quality: Quality is the integral part of our organization, and thus we undertake varied stringent measures throughout the manufacturing process. The quality of our products that we offer are closely monitored by our quality assurance professionals which is widely appreciated by our clients located across the world.

Client Satisfaction: The main objective of our organization is to attain the highest degree of client satisfaction. We have henceforth always used high quality raw materials which enables us to provide long-lasting products to our clients. These products are designed and configured as per the latest industrial norms which also shed light on the set industrial standards followed by us.

Why Us?/: We are a highly reputed manufacturer, supplier and service provider of the best cotton clippings, cotton clips and cotton wastes. These products are not only provided to our clients as per various specifications but also are offered at industry leading rates which is highly beneficial for our clients.
